title: Penguins finish preseason with 2-1 loss to Hurricanes
text:
Published By: Pittsburgh Post: Penguins - Today 
The Penguins finished their preseason with a 2-1 road loss to the Carolina Hurricanes at PNC Arena in Raleigh, N.C. tonight....
